				Pardon my ignorance, but I've heard about these EXP modifiers sever time, but have yet to see any documents that outline any racial/class differences.  Could someone write to me, or reply to this string, and direct me to a website that has these statistics or just spell it out for me themselves.  I'd appreciate knowing which races/classes gain the most EXP.<BR>
I would also like to know equations for the sharing of EXP in a group.  I was to assume that in a group of 6, if 600 EXP were to be gained, each person would get 100 EXP.  Apparently this is not the case, and that both level and class factor into the equation... but again... I've yet to see this statistic as well.<BR>
I'm sick of all these abstract and unverifiable claims.  I don't care if you 'think' something is the way it is; I want proof that something is how it is, beyond the experience of it.  There has to be a defining equation, there has to be a testable paradigm, and there has to be someone out there who knows it.
				</font>
			</td>

